remove any whitespace from returned string in substring removal

search is off by one in cases like this:

$>"echo ${PWD:+${PWD#/home}"
$>e/miika/workspace/42sh




----------TESTS------------

$> echo ${SHELL}
/bin/zsh
$>
---------------
$> echo ${PWD:+}

$>
---------------
$> echo ${PWD:-}
/Users/mviinika/workspace/42sh
$>
---------------
$> echo ${PWD:=}
/Users/mviinika/workspace/42sh
$>
---------------
$> echo ${PWD:?}
/Users/mviinika/workspace/42sh
$>
---------------


> echo ${PWD:+jee${PWD}}
> echo ${PWD}